OL,3,CHow can you avoid falling victim to a
OL,4,Cphone or online scam?
OL,6,FScammers have long targeted older
OL,7,Fpeople seeing them as easy victims but
OL,8,Fthis tactic may soon come to an end.
OL,10,FOlder people are the most likely group
OL,11,Fin Britain to talk back to scammers,
OL,12,Fnew research by BT Group and Ability
OL,13,FNet has revealed.
OL,15,FThe study revealed that 23% of older
OL,16,Fpeople surveyed - 2,000 in total -
OL,17,Fhave confronted scammers over the
OL,18,Fphone.
